  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      There is no definite evidence for the conservative treatment of pes planus. We want to verify
      the combination efficacy of orthosis and toe walking exercise for the treatment of pes
      planus.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Observation cohort study

      We prescribe UCBL orthosis and teach toe walking exercise. And we will check standing foot
      radiography (AP/Lateral) annually. And we will compare the changes of talometatarsal angle
      and calcaneal pitch angle.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
